name: com.castsoftware.aip.reportgeneratorfordashboard
title: ReportGenerator for Dashboards
description: The CAST Report Generator for Dahboard is a standalone service, that will be used by CAST Dashboards, for automatic generation of reports based on data generated by CAST AIP. The solution provides the opportunity (for example) to prepare and automate assessments for each new version of application analyzed with CAST AIP. Documents are based on Microsoft Office templates and they can be modified to prepare a specific template to meet a particular use case or to comply with a company format.
